/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a tranquil scene of a tree-lined street in Beijing, China. The perspective is from a low angle, giving a sense of depth and scale to the scene. The trees, stripped of their leaves, stand tall against the backdrop of a clear blue sky. Their bare branches reach out, creating a natural canopy over the street. The street itself is devoid of any vehicles or pedestrians, adding to the serene atmosphere. In the distance, a body of water can be seen, reflecting the sky and adding a touch of nature to the urban landscape. The image is bathed in the warm glow of the sun, casting long shadows and highlighting the textures of the trees and the road.
